50 enum SpellAuraInterruptFlags
51 {
52  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_HITBYSPELL = 0x00000001, // 0 removed when getting hit by a negative spell?
53  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_TAKE_DAMAGE = 0x00000002, // 1 removed by any damage
54  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_CAST = 0x00000004, // 2 cast any spells
55  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_MOVE = 0x00000008, // 3 removed by any movement
56  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_TURNING = 0x00000010, // 4 removed by any turning
57  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_JUMP = 0x00000020, // 5 removed by entering combat
58  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_NOT_MOUNTED = 0x00000040, // 6 removed by dismounting
59  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_NOT_ABOVEWATER = 0x00000080, // 7 removed by entering water
60  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_NOT_UNDERWATER = 0x00000100, // 8 removed by leaving water
61  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_NOT_SHEATHED = 0x00000200, // 9 removed by unsheathing
62  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_TALK = 0x00000400, // 10 talk to npc / loot? action on creature
63  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_USE = 0x00000800, // 11 mine/use/open action on gameobject
64  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_MELEE_ATTACK = 0x00001000, // 12 removed by attacking
65  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_SPELL_ATTACK = 0x00002000, // 13 ???
66  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_UNK14 = 0x00004000, // 14
67  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_TRANSFORM = 0x00008000, // 15 removed by transform?
68  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_UNK16 = 0x00010000, // 16
69  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_MOUNT = 0x00020000, // 17 misdirect, aspect, swim speed
70  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_NOT_SEATED = 0x00040000, // 18 removed by standing up (used by food and drink mostly and sleep/Fake Death like)
71  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_CHANGE_MAP = 0x00080000, // 19 leaving map/getting teleported
72  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_IMMUNE_OR_LOST_SELECTION = 0x00100000, // 20 removed by auras that make you invulnerable, or make other to lose selection on you
73  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_UNK21 = 0x00200000, // 21
74  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_TELEPORTED = 0x00400000, // 22
75  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_ENTER_PVP_COMBAT = 0x00800000, // 23 removed by entering pvp combat
76  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_DIRECT_DAMAGE = 0x01000000, // 24 removed by any direct damage
77  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_LANDING = 0x02000000, // 25 removed by hitting the ground
78  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_LEAVE_COMBAT = 0x80000000, // 31 removed by leaving combat
79 
80  AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_NOT_VICTIM = (AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_HITBYSPELL | AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_TAKE_DAMAGE | AURA_INTERRUPT_FLAG_DIRECT_DAMAGE),
81 };

940 class HealInfo
941 {
942 private:
943  Unit* const m_healer;
944  Unit* const m_target;
945  uint32 m_heal;
946  uint32 m_absorb;
947  SpellInfo const* const m_spellInfo;
948  SpellSchoolMask const m_schoolMask;
949 public:
950  explicit HealInfo(Unit* _healer, Unit* _target, uint32 _heal, SpellInfo const* _spellInfo, SpellSchoolMask _schoolMask)
951  : m_healer(_healer), m_target(_target), m_heal(_heal), m_spellInfo(_spellInfo), m_schoolMask(_schoolMask)
952  {
953  m_absorb = 0;
954  }
955  void AbsorbHeal(uint32 amount)
956  {
957  amount = std::min(amount, GetHeal());
958  m_absorb += amount;
959  m_heal -= amount;
960  }

1164 #define UNIT_ACTION_BUTTON_ACTION(X) (uint32(X) & 0x00FFFFFF)
1165 #define UNIT_ACTION_BUTTON_TYPE(X) ((uint32(X) & 0xFF000000) >> 24)
1166 #define MAKE_UNIT_ACTION_BUTTON(A, T) (uint32(A) | (uint32(T) << 24))
1167 
1168 struct UnitActionBarEntry
1169 {
1170  UnitActionBarEntry() : packedData(uint32(ACT_DISABLED) << 24) {}
1171 
1172  uint32 packedData;
1173 
1174  // helper
1175  [[nodiscard]] ActiveStates GetType() const { return ActiveStates(UNIT_ACTION_BUTTON_TYPE(packedData)); }
1176  [[nodiscard]] uint32 GetAction() const { return UNIT_ACTION_BUTTON_ACTION(packedData); }
1177  [[nodiscard]] bool IsActionBarForSpell() const
1178  {
1179  ActiveStates Type = GetType();
1180  return Type == ACT_DISABLED || Type == ACT_ENABLED || Type == ACT_PASSIVE;
1181  }
1182 
1183  void SetActionAndType(uint32 action, ActiveStates type)
1184  {
1185  packedData = MAKE_UNIT_ACTION_BUTTON(action, type);
1186  }
1187 
1188  void SetType(ActiveStates type)
1189  {
1190  packedData = MAKE_UNIT_ACTION_BUTTON(UNIT_ACTION_BUTTON_ACTION(packedData), type);
1191  }
1192 
1193  void SetAction(uint32 action)
1194  {
1195  packedData = (packedData & 0xFF000000) | UNIT_ACTION_BUTTON_ACTION(action);
1196  }
1197 };

1369 // pussywizard:
1370 class MMapTargetData

1374  MMapTargetData(uint32 endTime, const Position* o, const Position* t)

1377  _posOwner.Relocate(o);
1378  _posTarget.Relocate(t);
1379  }

1381  {

1383  _posOwner.Relocate(c._posOwner);
1384  _posTarget.Relocate(c._posTarget);
1385  }

1387 #if __cplusplus >= 201103L
1388  MMapTargetData(MMapTargetData&&) = default;
1389  MMapTargetData& operator=(const MMapTargetData&) = default;
1390  MMapTargetData& operator=(MMapTargetData&&) = default;
1391 #endif
1392  [[nodiscard]] bool PosChanged(const Position& o, const Position& t) const
1393  {
1394  return _posOwner.GetExactDistSq(&o) > 0.5f * 0.5f || _posTarget.GetExactDistSq(&t) > 0.5f * 0.5f;
1395  }
1396  uint32 _endTime;
1397  Position _posOwner;
1398  Position _posTarget;
1399 };

1713  case RANGED_ATTACK:

1719  [[nodiscard]] virtual uint32 GetShieldBlockValue() const = 0;
1720  [[nodiscard]] uint32 GetShieldBlockValue(uint32 soft_cap, uint32 hard_cap) const
1721  {
1722  uint32 value = GetShieldBlockValue();
1723  if (value >= hard_cap)
1724  {
1725  value = (soft_cap + hard_cap) / 2;
1726  }
1727  else if (value > soft_cap)
1728  {
1729  value = soft_cap + ((value - soft_cap) / 2);
1730  }
1731 
1732  return value;
1733  }

2659 {
2660  // Binary predicate for sorting Units based on percent value of a power
2661  class PowerPctOrderPred
2662  {
2663  public:
2664  PowerPctOrderPred(Powers power, bool ascending = true) : _power(power), _ascending(ascending) { }
2665 
2666  bool operator()(WorldObject const* objA, WorldObject const* objB) const
2667  {
2668  Unit const* a = objA->ToUnit();
2669  Unit const* b = objB->ToUnit();
2670  float rA = (a && a->GetMaxPower(_power)) ? float(a->GetPower(_power)) / float(a->GetMaxPower(_power)) : 0.0f;
2671  float rB = (b && b->GetMaxPower(_power)) ? float(b->GetPower(_power)) / float(b->GetMaxPower(_power)) : 0.0f;
2672  return _ascending ? rA < rB : rA > rB;
2673  }
2674 
2675  bool operator()(Unit const* a, Unit const* b) const
2676  {
2677  float rA = a->GetMaxPower(_power) ? float(a->GetPower(_power)) / float(a->GetMaxPower(_power)) : 0.0f;
2678  float rB = b->GetMaxPower(_power) ? float(b->GetPower(_power)) / float(b->GetMaxPower(_power)) : 0.0f;
2679  return _ascending ? rA < rB : rA > rB;
2680  }
2681 
2682  private:
2683  Powers const _power;
2684  bool const _ascending;
2685  };
2686 
2687  // Binary predicate for sorting Units based on percent value of health
2688  class HealthPctOrderPred
2689  {
2690  public:
2691  HealthPctOrderPred(bool ascending = true) : _ascending(ascending) { }
2692 
2693  bool operator()(WorldObject const* objA, WorldObject const* objB) const
2694  {
2695  Unit const* a = objA->ToUnit();
2696  Unit const* b = objB->ToUnit();
2697  float rA = (a && a->GetMaxHealth()) ? float(a->GetHealth()) / float(a->GetMaxHealth()) : 0.0f;
2698  float rB = (b && b->GetMaxHealth()) ? float(b->GetHealth()) / float(b->GetMaxHealth()) : 0.0f;
2699  return _ascending ? rA < rB : rA > rB;
2700  }
2701 
2702  bool operator() (Unit const* a, Unit const* b) const
2703  {
2704  float rA = a->GetMaxHealth() ? float(a->GetHealth()) / float(a->GetMaxHealth()) : 0.0f;
2705  float rB = b->GetMaxHealth() ? float(b->GetHealth()) / float(b->GetMaxHealth()) : 0.0f;
2706  return _ascending ? rA < rB : rA > rB;
2707  }
2708 
2709  private:
2710  bool const _ascending;
2711  };
2712 }
